Title: Creates an advisory group which shall produce a report on improving urban and rural consumer access to locally produced, healthy foods
Summary: Creates an advisory group which shall produce a report on improving urban and rural consumer access to locally produced, healthy foods; provides such group shall include representatives from agriculture, food access organizations, food retailers and economic development agencies; makes changes to the effectiveness.
LawCode: Amd ยง28, Ag & Mkts L; amd ยง2, Chap of 2021 (as proposed in S.1056 & A.4613)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, in relation to a report on improving urban and rural consumer access to locally produced, healthy foods, and to amend a chapter of the laws of 2021 amending the agriculture and markets law relating to the task force on improving urban and rural consumer access to locally produced, healthy foods, as proposed in legislative bills numbers S. 1056 and A. 4613, in relation to the effectiveness thereof
